    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IndexCommand.AddNodeCommand, IndexCommand.AddRelationshipCommand, IndexCommand.CreateCommand, IndexCommand.DeleteCommand, IndexCommand.RemoveCommand
    public abstract class IndexCommand
extends Command
    Created from IndexDefineCommand or read from a logical log. Contains all the different types of commands that an indexes need to support.
